<pre class="bz_comment_text">There is an integer overflow vulnerability in the DxeImageVerificationHandler(..) function when parsing the PE files attribute certificate table. In cases where WinCertificate-&gt;dwLength is sufficiently large, it's possible to overflow Offset back to 0 causing an endless loop.

There needs to be stricter validation of Offset and the embedded length fields of certificate data before using them to advance the loop.</pre>
    </div>

